               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols. 3ra-44vb),
                     incomplete
 II) Liturgical miscellanea (fols. 45r-56r)
 - Fǝtḥat
                     za-wald “Absolution of the Son” (fols. 44v-46v)</summary>
